.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講出街危險做網上戰線，twitter次次都係得嗰幾十人，用你啲口水去屌五毛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係識扮軍師屌黃店屌手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"借po 出channel  ok?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"隨便，叫啲鍵戰屌外人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"14f06a5b2c9fe2bb6b32c68c7554b00ed6f248b2","tid":1935972,"uid":345002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">藍絲一早出左張POSTER話打曱甴, 然後元朗唔關站,<br />\n原因係:<br />\n1. <ins>嚇和理非,唔敢出黎</ins><br />\n2. <ins>等勇武帶工具&quot;覆桌&quot; 原來係假既, 再大圍捕 &amp; SS 一獲拉晒</ins><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第2點,第2點,第2點<br />\n好重要, 好重要, 好重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次一定大班記者在場<br />\n我唔係好信再有721發生, 上次都未搞掂, 又黎一次, 班Popo死緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n721靜坐, 請唔好帶任何文具,<br />\n101% 逐個Check 唔好比Popo有藉口入拉你<br />\n<br />\n<ins>**建議只帶 背囊(放本書), 正常長遮/縮骨遮 (可能落雨),口罩,文宣,手機**</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*****唔該廣傳比各位手足*****</span></span>"},{"pid":"d05e26fea702d32789a8d2fbc890c33c67ddb106","tid":1935972,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"去邊都係送頭<br />\n留係屋企線上抗爭就最啱最安全最唔送頭<br />\n我有like 721 po冇忘記手足㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253cd752819452a0ac8ddbc210800027b1a09f11","tid":1935972,"uid":199261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"行動post 推唔起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a400bd57db48eb1f150fdd999595b5d1ff12d6","tid":1935972,"uid":102835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad43e6c4e5d7d53d9329a265077bc8a2c813a38d","tid":1935972,"uid":35429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"疫情期間，唔好集中去一個地方啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"有唔同站啦，至少銅鑼灣都有<br />\n我自己覺得大西北撚先好入元朗同睇人數行事<br />\n但人地入都唔駛屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fba08d49e5be3bbd7f40a5b338d82c568d5001","tid":1935972,"uid":4458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"真係谷鳩氣，屌你老尾咩？<br />\n<br />\n手足，你真會出嘅會唔會因為一兩個post決定出/唔出呀而家？<br />\n<br />\n大西北撚會出，你唔出咪唔出駛唔駛又屌送頭？<br />\n<br />\n六月尾狗總屌到依家仲係唔明每位手足都有自己意志？唔明你自己可以決定自己去邊。<br />\n<br />\n你覺得冇用咪推其他行動囉，咪玩其他戰線囉屌<br />\n<br />\n咪撚當手足都係戇鳩，冇諗過你講嘅危險至得架<br />\n<br />\n等睇啲戇鳩叫sir?<br />\n<br />\nSir你老母咩，日鳩日話咩出街危險啊，會送頭呀，叫人做網上戰線，國際戰線。<br />\n<br />\n結果呢？twitter次次都係得嗰幾十人玩，戰線？<br />\n<br />\n香港鍵戰用你啲口水去屌五毛吹抗爭好過啦，淨係識扮軍師屌黃店屌手足。<br />\n<br />\n#歷史撚 #谷鳩氣"},{"pid":"febcdd22ecedc5d6ab890ed051a57c455b8040b0","tid":1935972,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0261b08ebd75f3a4d2b82edccb9c3edaa6293478","tid":1935972,"uid":99876,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"點解明知d鄉黑ready哂都仲要去送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(我覺得) 呢幾日確診真係急升，出去就變左同佢地一樣on9<br />\n但為左唔好熄左團火，可以online做其他野(?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b948b939f9644c74b620155ace556686ca239e","tid":1935972,"uid":64120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"要打都唔係入元朗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaa98aa3643bb966d70d56116e5e189e82ac24d","tid":1935972,"uid":311461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"唔去元朗咪銅鑼灣"},{"pid":"2721f51b96a6242aaeec643d45b61172902a3e94","tid":1935972,"uid":3456